{"tid":1091424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子鞋底藏500克毒品麻古 一個月不洗腳圖腳臭避安檢","createTime":"2019-04-04T06:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T16:29:14.000Z","uid":75969,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7782c225906bc3a136ac0da907fa1637002f8b2b","tid":1091424,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190403/_2019040322470473113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190403%2F_2019040322470473113.jpg&h=488b41b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190403/_2019040322470474676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190403%2F_2019040322470474676.jpg&h=b89638a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南京警方近日在機場拘捕一名攜帶共500克毒品麻古入境的男子。他將毒品藏在鞋底，而且一個月沒洗腳，企圖以臭味躲避安檢。<br />\n<br />\n南京警方根據情報，一名來自雲南的楊姓男子將從境外攜帶毒品，並將在南京轉機，於是在安檢閘機旁將他拘捕。誰料，當民警用X光機檢測時，在他身上卻沒有發現任何可疑物品。在民警陷入僵局時，突然發現他穿了一雙很薄的運動鞋，而且沒穿襪子，而且「腳很臭」，隨即將其鞋子脫下，並在兩隻鞋子的夾層中發現各藏了10包麻古，總重將近500克。<br />\n<br />\n經調查後，原來<span style=\"color: red;\">楊男從一個月前開始不但穿鞋不穿襪子，而且亦不洗腳，加上他本身的腳容易出汗，因此企圖以臭味躲避安檢。據民警指，在拘捕楊男時，離遠3、4米已能聞到其腳臭味。</span>目前，楊男涉嫌非法持有毒品罪被刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/972379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F972379&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=91879246\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F972379&h=08faa3ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/972379</a>"},{"pid":"afb7c3ab19d73cdf551b202657d5e3bed181fef9","tid":1091424,"uid":130695,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"隔住個mon..."},{"pid":"7cff34c700657a102e8c3f3223213a377279cdf9","tid":1091424,"uid":149383,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"雲南腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051deda274a6d8c2e25debdb2b8272cdb371272c","tid":1091424,"uid":153239,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"在拘捕楊男時，離遠3、4米已能聞到其腳臭味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6544ee57af091f3097b2d781e48b946fdb97d4","tid":1091424,"uid":101110,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:23:31.000Z","msg":"「在目前流行的海洛因、冰毒、麻古、K粉中，只有麻古才會有劇烈的香味。有麻古成癮戒毒者描述，此種香味不同於平常生活中的香味，有點類似香草，又象似桂花或是奶香。」<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正毒上加毒"},{"pid":"0fbe1ad9095dcb7b09fe7a9803bc17d3467fde56","tid":1091424,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"安檢X光睇唔到有毒品又會知佢身上有毒品？"},{"pid":"19671f7f2e4415f51e0e51334fcc422252fa86fe","tid":1091424,"uid":21598,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0fbe1ad9095dcb7b09fe7a9803bc17d3467fde56","tid":1091424,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"安檢X光睇唔到有毒品又會知佢身上有毒品？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"南京警方根據情報，一名來自雲南的楊姓男子將從境外攜帶毒品，並將在南京轉機，於是在安檢閘機旁將他拘捕。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281834d3fa5286ff02f1aa975cd6d66463664357","tid":1091424,"uid":233237,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"0fbe1ad9095dcb7b09fe7a9803bc17d3467fde56","tid":1091424,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"安檢X光睇唔到有毒品又會知佢身上有毒品？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:27:51.000Z","msg":"X光驗到，但人手搵唔到"},{"pid":"48494cb8a928a0570dd1d8d3729c7e18db544e58","tid":1091424,"uid":123456,"like":7,"dislike":3,"scor